        "florence-street": {
            "id": "florence-street",
            "summary": "They see Renaissance Florence alive with art, commerce, and ideas",
            "text": "{{BOTH_NAMES}} take in the incredible scene. Florence in 1504 is alive with energy!\n\nArtists carry canvases through the streets. Merchants sell pigments in every color imaginable‚Äîground lapis lazuli for brilliant blue, crushed beetles for deep red, gold leaf thin as a whisper. A sculptor chips at a block of white marble in an open workshop.\n\n'This is the Renaissance,' Giuliano says proudly. 'It means rebirth. For a thousand years, art stood still. Now, we're rediscovering what the ancient Greeks and Romans knew‚Äîand going beyond them.'\n\nHe points to a massive dome rising above the rooftops. 'Brunelleschi's dome. They said it was impossible to build, but he did it anyway. That's the spirit of our age: nothing is impossible if you have skill, knowledge, and courage.'\n\n{{PLAYER1_NAME}} sees people arguing passionately on a corner. 'What are they debating?'\n\n'Ideas! Art! Philosophy! In Florence, everyone cares about beauty and truth. Even the bankers and merchants are patrons of art. The Medici family funds half the artists in the city!'",
